Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:52.63,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,The starlight we’ve been searching for is being plucked away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:58.37,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Perhaps from the very start, the shadow of the end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:03.28,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,was watching us from the depths of our dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:08.34,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Hiding an empty heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:12.49,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,I keep searching for the meaning of sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:16.26,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,The fireworks bursting inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:20.15,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,stain our vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:24.25,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Repeating—taking everything away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.59,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Aimlessly, the branches stretch out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:34.68,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Bringing the stagnant pain of this trampled world into focus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.29,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Unceasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:39.47,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Now, as we stand face to face, we lose—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.77,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Everything has vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.72,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,My heart now drifts through the void
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.82,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,At the core, everything is intertwined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.35,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,forming a complete light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:55.25,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,But if we stay like this, even our destination will fade
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:00.23,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,Without stopping, we heal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.94,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,So light that I barely noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:11.37,OP/EN,,0,0,0,,regret now carves a hole inside me
